Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快看 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我抓到独角仙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,独角仙？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就像昆虫里的国王一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大只
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找的是音符喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,虫子先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到音符了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,OK喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,席利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,阿喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么没什么精神呀喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我没事 Sisi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那进行回收吧喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,席利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,席利他们是不是中暑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哎喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大家没事吧 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 Sisi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让音调精灵们好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要收集更多的音符喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:00:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,独角仙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才抓到的那只吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,开学以后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去给班上的同学看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假已经快结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉转眼间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,呃！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,“垒球大赛”就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要和甜点部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,想出新口味的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一起为“文化祭”准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩都不会寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是开学了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,学校与暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有着不同的快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以见到同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还有社团的伙伴等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,各种各样的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的作业做完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,今年有好好做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是有在成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,奏君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲的初次学校生活喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,今天貌似也会很热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真难相信明天就开学了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有音符的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让哈米她们发现 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就只能靠我们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,用自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把那个音符夺回来 Rere
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才说了什么吗 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什...什么也没说 Rere
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要在家里休息 Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,关于艾莲去学校的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去和爸爸商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,能有什么好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以去学校上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,其实今天早上...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,制服和书包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,亚莉亚学园中学部的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非可以让我去学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,从明天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,享受学校生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,音吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让艾莲去学校上学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,音吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越是个谜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有好多不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有些不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那来排练一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们教你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,与中学有关的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,飞蛾扑火作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,说来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的领队不是弗赛托吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯多拉说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要做领队不听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,前几天抢来的这些音符
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,应该会来夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把抢来的音符放在这个瓶子里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,引诱她们出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近这个瓶子的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,笼子从上面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这样她们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就没办法逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,中学是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,从早上开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,午休过后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,继续上课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,或是参加社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,上课 午休
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,上课 社团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,午休的时候吃便当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,天气晴朗的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在院子里吃超美味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,午休吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,天气晴朗 在院子里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一年当中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,会举办运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,郊游等很多好玩的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,运动会 文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你去了学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再慢慢开始了解也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从自我介绍的练习开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次进教室的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要向大家打招呼喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,让你看哈米的示范喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是哈米？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米的名字叫哈米喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米的名字叫哈米...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这个当然知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为了完成幸福的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和这些音调精灵们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,收集音符喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,阿勒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,音调精灵不在喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就没看见她们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,之前他们说回家去了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我们担心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米最喜欢杯蛋糕喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都想吃很多喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢杯蛋糕...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不用记在笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米爪子的肉垫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,摸起来很舒服喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,奏喜欢摸哈米的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,肉垫是最喜欢了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事不用说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奏喜欢摸肉垫...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也不用记下来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了吸引注意而唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,唱歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,唱歌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米很喜欢喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喵呀呀哑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喵呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米 不用唱啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,唱歌...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你不要记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,发现音符 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比起光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可以得到更多音符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那树下有好多音符 Rere
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大家把音符带走 Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Soso Sisi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,万岁！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,大 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快点逃跑 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodo Rere Sisi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,呀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fafa fa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嘿嘿的嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,救他们 Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑 Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,做自我介绍的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让大家看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在黑板上将名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,写得大大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,介绍下自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我没叫喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,阿勒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,又听见那个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在叫“响”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别说这么吓人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是音吉先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是女孩子的声音呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,响是不是也有点中暑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,自我介绍没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉越想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,越紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想要表达自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲只要做平时的艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会喜欢上艾莲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 喵...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,黑川艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没穿制服了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,响呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,勉强算是完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脸是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚紧张得睡不着觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们送你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,手帕和铅笔盒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,代替护身符使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中的节拍止不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊锵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我们做下自我介绍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,初...初次见面！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是“黑川艾莲”！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,声音太大了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢的食物是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,声音可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微小一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好...好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢的食物是杯蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的颜色是蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的动物是猫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米的自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,原封不动照抄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,充满音乐风情的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴能进入这个中学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想为大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,唱首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,咦嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,都在为我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,黑川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再听你的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好...好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,叱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,作战本来很完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要收集些音符了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢什么运动？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,喂...稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都没办法接近她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,运动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有特别擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都想试试看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢黑猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经是只黑猫...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,天上有飞碟！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前住在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小调岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前是大调...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 哇哇哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我是住在一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做幸运小勺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,的糕饼店里哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你之前住在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是住在小调...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来为下一堂课做准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正如
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,响所说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,能问黑川一些事情
